{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-313-sliding-game","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 313: Igra pomeranja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U igri pomeranja pločica, pločica se može pomeriti horizontalno ili vertikalno u prazno polje. Cilj igre je pomeriti svetlu pločicu iz gornjeg levog ugla mreže do donjeg desnog ugla; prazno polje uvek počinje u donjem desnom uglu. Na primer, sledeći niz slika pokazuje kako se igra može završiti u pet koraka na mreži od 2 na 2.</p>\n<img alt=\"completing game in five moves on grid 2x2\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sliding-game-1.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka $S(m, n)$ predstavlja minimalan broj koraka za završavanje igre na mreži od $m$ po $n$. Na primer, može se dokazati da je $S(5, 4) = 25$.</p>\n<img alt=\"initial grid state and final grid state for game on grid 5x4\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/sliding-game-2.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Postoje mreže 5482 koje su $S(m, n) = p^2$, gde je $p &#x3C; 100$ prim brojac.</p>\n<p>Koliko grilova postoji takvih da je $S(m, n) = p^2$, gde je $p &#x3C; {10}^6$ prost broj?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4a61000cf542c50ffb8","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301969,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-313-sliding-game"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"file